    "content": "다음 그림과 같이 중심이 $O$, 반지름의 길이가 1인 사분원의 호 $PQ$를 9등분하는 점을 차례로 $P_1,\\ P_2,\\ \\cdots,\\ P_8$이라고 하자. 점 $P_1,\\ P_2,\\ \\cdots,\\ P_8$에서 선분 $OP$에 내린 수선의 발을 각각 $Q_1,\\ Q_2,\\ \\cdots,\\ Q_8$이라고 할 때, $\\overline{OQ_1}^{\\,2}+\\overline{OQ_2}^{\\,2}+\\overline{OQ_3}^{\\,2}+\\cdots+\\overline{OQ_8}^{\\,2}$의 값은? [4.5점]<br><br><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><svg width=\"215\" height=\"190\" viewBox=\"0 0 215 190\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M 35 155 L 185 155\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><path d=\"M 35 155 L 35 5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><path d=\"M 35 5 A 150 150 0 0 1 185 155\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><g stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"><line x1=\"35\" y1=\"155\" x2=\"61.0\" y2=\"7.3\"/><line x1=\"35\" y1=\"155\" x2=\"86.3\" y2=\"14.0\"/><line x1=\"35\" y1=\"155\" x2=\"110.0\" y2=\"25.1\"/><line x1=\"35\" y1=\"155\" x2=\"131.4\" y2=\"40.1\"/><line x1=\"35\" y1=\"155\" x2=\"149.9\" y2=\"58.5\"/><line x1=\"35\" y1=\"155\" x2=\"165.0\" y2=\"80.0\"/><line x1=\"35\" y1=\"155\" x2=\"176.0\" y2=\"103.7\"/><line x1=\"35\" y1=\"155\" x2=\"182.7\" y2=\"129.0\"/></g><g stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"0.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"2 1\" opacity=\"0.4\"><line x1=\"61\" y1=\"7\" x2=\"61\" y2=\"155\"/><line x1=\"86\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"86\" y2=\"155\"/><line x1=\"110\" y1=\"25\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"155\"/><line x1=\"131\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"131\" y2=\"155\"/><line x1=\"150\" y1=\"58\" x2=\"150\" y2=\"155\"/><line x1=\"165\" y1=\"80\" x2=\"165\" y2=\"155\"/><line x1=\"176\" y1=\"104\" x2=\"176\" y2=\"155\"/><line x1=\"183\" y1=\"129\" x2=\"183\" y2=\"155\"/></g><text x=\"22\" y=\"168\" font-size=\"10px\" font-family=\"serif\">O</text><text x=\"187\" y=\"168\" font-size=\"10px\" font-family=\"serif\">P</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"10\" font-size=\"10px\" font-family=\"serif\">Q</text><g font-size=\"9px\" font-family=\"serif\"><text x=\"58\" y=\"6\">P₁</text><text x=\"83\" y=\"11\">P₂</text><text x=\"108\" y=\"22\">P₃</text><text x=\"129\" y=\"37\">P₄</text><text x=\"147\" y=\"55\">P₅</text><text x=\"162\" y=\"77\">P₆</text><text x=\"173\" y=\"100\">P₇</text><text x=\"180\" y=\"126\">P₈</text><text x=\"61\" y=\"168\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Q₁</text><text x=\"86\" y=\"168\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Q₂</text><text x=\"110\" y=\"168\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Q₃</text><text x=\"131\" y=\"168\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Q₄</text><text x=\"150\" y=\"168\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Q₅</text><text x=\"165\" y=\"168\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Q₆</text><text x=\"176\" y=\"168\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Q₇</text><text x=\"183\" y=\"168\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Q₈</text></g><text x=\"110\" y=\"150\" font-size=\"10px\" font-family=\"serif\">1</text></svg></div>",
